text.__SUMMARY__: Ceratozamia huastecorum is a species of cycad in the family Zamiaceae endemic to a small area of northern Veracruz, Mexico.
text.References: Whitelock, Loran M. 2002. The Cycads. Portland: Timber Press. ISBN 0-88192-522-5
